    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这是一条测试博客。</p><h1 id="测试一级标题"><a href="#测试一级标题" class="headerlink" title="测试一级标题"></a>测试一级标题</h1><h2 id="二级标题"><a href="#二级标题" class="headerlink" title="二级标题"></a>二级标题</h2><h3 id="三级标题"><a href="#三级标题" class="headerlink" title="三级标题"></a>三级标题</h3><h4 id="四级标题"><a href="#四级标题" class="headerlink" title="四级标题"></a>四级标题</h4><h5 id="五级标题"><a href="#五级标题" class="headerlink" title="五级标题"></a>五级标题</h5><h6 id="六级标题"><a href="#六级标题" class="headerlink" title="六级标题"></a>六级标题</h6><p>段落换行:<br>使用两个及以上空格加回车。</p><h2 id="分割线、列表与TODO"><a href="#分割线、列表与TODO" class="headerlink" title="分割线、列表与TODO"></a>分割线、列表与TODO</h2><h2 id="分割线"><a href="#分割线" class="headerlink" title="分割线"></a>分割线</h2><hr><ul><li>无序列表1</li><li>无序列表2</li></ul><ol><li>有序列表1</li><li>有序列表2</li></ol><ul><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Todo</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> Done</li></ul><h2 id="字体格式"><a href="#字体格式" class="headerlink" title="字体格式"></a>字体格式</h2><p><strong>加粗</strong><br><em>斜体</em><br><em><strong>加粗斜体</strong></em><br><del>删除线</del><br><u>下划线</u></p><p style="text-align:center">文字居中显示。</p><font color="blue">文字颜色</font><h2 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h2><blockquote><p>引用内容<br>最外层</p><blockquote><p>第一层嵌套</p><blockquote><p>第二层嵌套</p></blockquote></blockquote><ol><li>有序列表1</li><li>有序列表2</li></ol><ul><li>无序列表1</li><li>无序列表2</li></ul></blockquote><blockquote><p>多个段落的引用，第一段</p><p>第二段</p></blockquote><ol><li>列表中使用引用</li><li>第二项<blockquote><p>引用外层</p><blockquote><p>嵌套</p></blockquote></blockquote></li><li>第三项</li><li>第四项</li></ol><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><p>stata代码</p><figure class="highlight stata"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">clear</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">sysuse</span> auto</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">des</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">keep</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> rep78 &gt; 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">clear</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>R代码</p><figure class="highlight r"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rm<span class="punctuation">(</span><span class="built_in">list</span> <span class="operator">=</span> ls<span class="punctuation">(</span><span class="punctuation">)</span><span class="punctuation">)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#install.packages(&quot;haven&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line">library<span class="punctuation">(</span>haven<span class="punctuation">)</span></span><br><span class="line">library<span class="punctuation">(</span>APCI<span class="punctuation">)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="链接与图片"><a href="#链接与图片" class="headerlink" title="链接与图片"></a>链接与图片</h2><p>这是一条测试链接：<a href="https://markdown.com.cn/">Markdown语法</a><br>可点击链接：<a href="https://markdown.com.cn/">https://markdown.com.cn</a></p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2025/10/12/ZQ6lF4G8MEA7uwH.png" width = "300" height = "300" alt="头像" align=center /><h2 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h2><table><thead><tr><th align="left">左对齐</th><th align="center">居中</th><th align="right">右对齐</th><th>默认</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">内容</td><td align="center">内容</td><td align="right">内容</td><td>内容</td></tr><tr><td align="left">内容2</td><td align="center">内容2</td><td align="right">内容</td><td>内容</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
    
    
